cs.LG, cs.MA, cs.AI, cs.GT, cs.SY

This paper proposes a novel coordination module for multi-agent reinforcement learning (MARL) and evaluates its performance in various games. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also discusses the concept of correlated equilibrium, which falls under the category of game theory (cs.GT). Finally, the proposed coordination module involves a centralized controller and decentralized agents, which can be seen as a system control problem (cs.SY).
